# InstaWork in EOD `index.html`

- InstaWork JPG save must call **`https://eod-api.the-dump-bin.com/instawork/save-image`** via **`authFetch()`** (not raw `fetch` to localhost). Same JSON body as before (`storeNumber`, `workDate`, `imageBase64`).
- Do not change this to `127.0.0.1:3001`; mobile browsers will always fail against localhost.
